## Modelos Eloquent

Dominio: `app/Domain/Assistant/Models/`

| Modelo | Tabla | Notas |
|---|---|---|
| `Conversation` | `assistant_conversations` | hasMany sessions, hasMany messages |
| `AssistantSession` | `assistant_sessions` | belongsTo conversation, hasMany messages |
| `AssistantMessage` | `assistant_messages` | belongsTo conversation + session; morphMedia (Spatie) |
| `Memory` | `memories` | belongsTo user |
| `TypeCatalog` | `type_catalogs` | belongsTo user nullable; no timestamps |
| `AssistantEvent` | `assistant_events` | belongsTo user; hasMany eventReminders; SoftDeletes |
| `EventReminder` | `event_reminders` | belongsTo event |
| `AssistantList` | `assistant_lists` | belongsTo user; hasMany items (order by position); hasMany shares; SoftDeletes |
| `ListItem` | `list_items` | belongsTo list |
| `Expense` | `expenses` | belongsTo user |
| `Friendship` | `friendships` | belongsTo requester (user), addressee (user) |
| `FriendLabel` | `friend_labels` | belongsTo user, belongsTo friend (user) |
| `ListShare` | `list_shares` | belongsTo list; belongsTo sharedWith, invitedBy (users); no timestamps |
| `ReminderRequest` | `reminder_requests` | belongsTo sender, receiver (user); belongsTo event, message (nullable) |

