## `friend_code` — generación

En `RegisterUseCase`, antes de `User::create()`:

```php
do {
    $friendCode = strtoupper(Str::random(8));
} while (User::where('friend_code', $friendCode)->exists());

$user = User::create([..., 'friend_code' => $friendCode]);
```

